HOLIDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Today is Thanksgiving Day. Among the closures for the holiday: 
</P>
<P>
 * Closed today: All government offices, courts, banks, post offices, stock and 
commodity exchanges, libraries, schools, many businesses and Metrolink 
trains.MTA buses will follow Sunday schedules. 
</P>
<P>
 * Closed Friday: Schools and all city, county, state and federal offices, 
courts and libraries. 
</P>
<P>
 * Open Friday: Post offices, banks, stock and commodity exchanges, Metrolink 
trains and the county law library. MTA buses will follow regular schedules. 
</P>
