</P>
<P>
 A semiautomatic handgun believed to have been used in the robbery was 
recovered at the scene. 
</P>
<P>
 The young man who was treated and released from the hospital and the 
15-year-old girl were taken to Los Padrinos Juvenile Hall in Norwalk. 
</P>
<P>
 Members of the rival group escaped. 
