</P>
<P>
 IN LAGUNA BEACH: 'INSPECTING CAROL' 
</P>
<P>
 Fresh, topical and outrageously funny, this backstage Christmas farce at the 
Laguna Playhouse's Moulton Theater (through Dec. 18) is a savvy lampoon of all 
those boilerplate stagings of "A Christmas Carol" that show up at this time of 
year. 606 Laguna Canyon Road. (714) 494-8021 .  
</P>
