 IN COSTA MESA: 'JAR THE FLOOR' 
</P>
<P>
 In Cheryl L. West's comedy-drama, a legacy of hostility and love is explored 
among four generations of strong-willed African-American women who gather for 
the matriarch's 80th birthday. Performed by a gifted cast, through Dec. 4. 
South Coast Repertory, 655 Town Center Drive. (714) 957-4033). 
