</P>
<P>
 Arthur Miller's historical drama about the notorious witch trials in 
17th-Century Massachusetts is a singularly great American play brought off with 
muscular flair in a vigorous, thoughtful, intense performance. Through Dec. 3 
at the Vanguard Theatre, 699 S. State College Blvd. (714) 526-8007. 
</P>
