<P>
BOYS' BASKETBALL 1994-1995: ORANGE LEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 WESTERN 03,17,09,08 1993-94 RECORDS OVERALL LEAGUE 11-14 2-8 COACH: Conrad 
Byars 
</P>
<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 0-0 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. HGT. P Paul 
Lindemeyer Sr. 6-4 C Richard Mackie Sr. 6-0 G 04,18,05,06,04 TOP RETURNERS YR. 
HGT. P Vince Bransetter Jr. 6-4 F Mike Freeman Jr. 6-1 G Bret Halbert Jr. 6-3 F 
Gilbert Issaian Sr. 5-7 G Brett Vernon Sr. 6-2 G 04,18,05,06,04 TOP NEWCOMERS 
YR. HGT. P Josh Burdett Jr. 6-1 F Anthony Casillas Jr. 6-1 F OUTLOOK 
