<P>
 Court Freezes British Executive's Assets: A federal judge, acting on a request 
from the Securities and Exchange Commission, froze the assets of Jeffrey 
Morris, who allegedly made illegal profits from the sale of Hilton Hotels Corp. 
stock. An SEC lawsuit alleged that Morris, 35, of Leeds, England, made an 
