 Fox & Carskadon Up For Sale: Fox & Carskadon, Northern California's largest 
residential real estate firm, is up for sale following a long, drawn-out 
dispute among its two partners. Majority partner Frank Luppi has filed for 
Chapter 11 bankruptcy protection and plans to sell his 75% interest in the 
company, Fox & Carskadon Chairman Richard Purvis said.The decision comes after 
a failure to settle a 17-month-old lawsuit filed against Luppi by former Fox & 
