</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The franchise arm of Coldwell Banker Corp., the Mission Viejo real estate 
brokerage, is one of the top 10 franchisers in North America, according to a 
recent survey. 
</P>
<P>
 The survey, published in the November issue of Success magazine, ranks 
Coldwell Banker Residential Affiliates Inc. among the top 10 franchise 
organizations for the second consecutive year. 
</P>
