corporate stability, franchiser attitude and services and relationships with 
franchisees. 
</P>
<P>
 Coldwell Banker Residential Affiliates Inc. has grown from 142 franchises in 
1982 to 2,029 franchises this year. It is a subsidiary of Coldwell Banker 
Corp., which has more than 2,300 residential real estate offices and 53,000 
employees. 
