<HEADLINE>
<P>
DOUGLAS, NELSON TO STAR IN 'TAKE ME HOME' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Kirk Douglas and Craig T. Nelson are teamed as father and son in "Take Me Home 
Again," a TV movie that NBC will broadcast Dec. 18. 
</P>
<P>
 The film was written by Ernest Thompson, who won an Oscar for "On Golden 
Pond." It's about an estranged son who patches up his differences with his 
father while traveling to the older man's birthplace. 
</P>
</TEXT>
